V0011_01_00_00_1.text: Let's hope this isn't the final game you'll ever play.

V0011_01_00_01_0.text: Challenging me to a Duel is your first - and last - mistake.

V0011_01_00_03_0.text: Talk it up while you can...

V0011_01_00_03_1.text: You'll be the one living in eternal darkness.

V0011_01_00_04_0.text: Every game has an end. It's just a question of who the victor will be.

V0011_01_00_04_1.text: And who will spend eternity roaming the Shadow Realm!

V0011_01_00_05_0.text: If you manage to defeat me, you're free to go. But lose and the only place you'll go is the Shadow Realm!

V0011_03_00_01_0.text: You have no chance for victory!

V0011_05_00_00_0.text: This card is just what I need to bury you in the shadows.

V0011_08_00_00_0.text: Five simple letters will spell your doom...

V0011_08_00_00_1.text: I activate the Continuous Trap, Destiny Board!

V0011_08_00_01_0.text: I activate Contract with the Dark Master!

V0011_08_00_02_0.text: The Spell Card, The Dark Door!

V0011_08_00_03_0.text: My face-down card is Dark Spirit of the Silent!

V0011_08_00_04_0.text: I activate my Continuous Trap, Macro Cosmos!

V0011_08_00_04_1.text: So unfortunate... How can you discard a card when you have no Graveyard to discard to?

V0011_08_00_05_0.text: I activate my Continuous Trap, Dimensional Fissure!

V0011_08_00_06_0.text: My Trap Card activates! Zoma the Spirit!

V0011_08_00_07_0.text: If a monster destroys this card, you take damage equal to that monster's Attack Points!

V0011_08_00_08_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Ectoplasmer!

V0011_08_00_09_1.text: You take damage equal to half the Attack Points of the Tributed monster!

V0011_08_00_10_1.text: We each return 1 monster from our Graveyards to the field.

V0011_11_00_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Attack Position!

V0011_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0011_13_00_00_0.text: I Summon the one that will cause your demise...

V0011_13_00_02_0.text: Dark Master - Zorc's resurrection is at hand!

V0011_13_00_05_0.text: I Special Summon Zoma the Spirit in Defense Position!

V0011_17_00_01_0.text: I attack you with a monster!

V0011_16_00_00_0.text: You're teetering on the edge of the Shadow Realm!

V0011_18_00_01_0.text: My monster attacks your Life Points directly!

V0011_19_00_02_0.text: I attack with Dark Master - Zorc!

V0011_19_00_03_1.text: Swing your blade to strike down your foes!

V0011_28_00_00_0.text: Hahaha... I hear the Shadow Realm's lovely this time of year.

V0011_28_00_00_1.text: You'll find out if it's true!

V0011_28_00_01_0.text: Heheheh... Did you actually believe that you could defeat me?

V0011_29_00_00_1.text: I will let you have this victory.

V0011_29_00_01_0.text: This can't be! How can I lose to the likes of you?

V0011_29_00_03_0.text: You haven't seen the last of me.

V0011_29_00_04_0.text: I wouldn't be celebrating if I were you.

V0011_29_00_04_1.text: I'll be back to show you that your victory was all in vain!

V0011_30_00_00_0.text: Aaaaahahahahaha! Too stunned to do anything?

V0011_30_00_01_0.text: Don't tell me that it's taken you this long to realize that you cannot win.

V0011_30_00_02_0.text: If you want to run away like a coward, this is your chance!

V0011_33_00_01_0.text: I have you right where I want you!

V0011_34_00_01_0.text: You will wander the darkness until the end of time!

V0011_34_00_02_0.text: You have no idea what I have in store next!

V0011_34_00_06_0.text: You can do less than nothing!

V0011_34_00_07_0.text: If that's the best you can do, then I've already won.

V0011_34_00_08_0.text: Aaahahaha! Don't be scared! Attack me!

V0011_34_00_09_0.text: You fell right into my trap!

V0011_26_00_02_0.text: Hmph... Is that the best you can do?

V0011_08_00_12_0.text: Destiny Board will write a special message just for you!

V0011_08_00_13_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Dark Spirit's Mastery!

V0011_08_00_14_0.text: I banish Dark Spirit's Mastery from the Graveyard!

V0011_08_00_15_0.text: You'll learn just how ghastly my occult combo is!

V0011_08_00_15_1.text:
I activate my Field Spell!
Dark Sanctuary!

V0011_08_00_17_0.text:
Heh heh heh...
I'll use this to take your card!

V0011_08_00_19_0.text:
Do you want a card?
Allow me to grant your wish!

V0011_08_00_20_0.text: I have the perfect card for this situation!

V0011_08_00_21_0.text: This card has predicted your demise!

V0011_08_00_21_1.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Sentence of Doom!

V0011_08_00_22_0.text: I activate Sentence of Doom's effect!

V0011_08_00_23_0.text: The Trap Card, Call of the Earthbound!

V0011_08_00_24_1.text: Any card I return to your deck can't threaten me!

V0011_40_00_02_0.text:
What!?
This wasn't supposed to happen!

V0011_09_00_06_0.text: I activate Dark Spirit of Banishment's effect!

V0011_09_00_07_0.text: I activate Dark Spirit of Malice's effect!

V0011_09_00_10_0.text: When Sangan goes to the Graveyard, its effect activates!

V0011_09_00_11_0.text: Gernia's effect activates from the Graveyard!

V0011_09_00_12_0.text:
Hahaha!
I activate Tragoedia's effect from my hand!

V0011_09_00_15_0.text: Puppet Master's effect activates when it's summoned!

V0011_09_00_16_0.text: I activate Jowgen the Spiritualist's effect!

V0011_09_00_17_0.text: White Magical Hat's effect forces you to discard a card!

V0011_13_00_07_0.text:
The conqueror of the afterlife!
Curse Necrofear!

V0011_13_00_14_0.text:
The fiend from the village of Kul Elna is here!
Tragoedia!

V0011_13_00_20_0.text:
This is the card I wanted!
Headless Knight!

V0011_13_00_22_0.text: The Gross Ghost of Fled Dreams!

V0011_13_00_24_0.text:
I'll play this card!
White Magical Hat!

V0011_19_00_16_0.text:
The Earl of Demise attacks!
Feel the sharpness of its blade!

V0011_19_00_17_0.text:
Headless Knight!
Slash them to shreds!

V0011_19_00_19_0.text: The Gross Ghost of Fled Dreams attacks!

V0011_19_00_20_0.text: Drag them into the ground, Earthbound Spirit!

V0011_19_00_22_0.text:
Dark Ruler Ha Des!
End their existence!
